<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Connect Skills</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.5/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-SgOJa3DmI69IUzQ2PVdRZhwQ+dy64/BUtbMJw1MZ8t5HZApcHrRKUc4W0kG879m7" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/shared/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/shared/home.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/img/CONNECT.png?v=2">
  </head>
  <body id="home">
    <main style="margin-top: 0; padding-top: 0;">
      <% var sucesso = typeof sucesso !== 'undefined' ? sucesso : false; %>
      <% var erro = typeof erro !== 'undefined' ? erro : false; %>
      
      <%- include('../partials/header-empresa') %>
      <div id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="/img/Banner.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- COMO FUNCIONA -->
      <section class="container my-5">
        <h3>
          Encontre o profissional certo para sua empresa, 
          <span class="text-primary" style="font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit;">
            de forma rápida e eficiente!
          </span>
        </h3>

        <p><strong>Como Funciona?</strong></p>
        <p>No Connect Skills, facilitamos a conexão entre empresas e talentos ideais. Utilize nossa tecnologia para encontrar candidatos que realmente fazem a diferença no seu time!</p>

        <div class="row g-4 mt-4">
          <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
            <div class="card text-center shadow-sm p-4 rounded-3 h-100 d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
              <div class="circle bg-primary text-white rounded-circle fw-bold mb-3"
                   style="width: 60px; height: 60px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                1
              </div>
              <p class="flex-grow-1">Cadastre sua empresa gratuitamente e acesse o painel para começar a recrutar talentos.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
            <div class="card text-center shadow-sm p-4 rounded-3 h-100 d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
              <div class="circle bg-primary text-white rounded-circle fw-bold mb-3"
                   style="width: 60px; height: 60px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                2
              </div>
              <p class="flex-grow-1">Publique vagas com informações e áreas de interesse desejadas.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
            <div class="card text-center shadow-sm p-4 rounded-3 h-100 d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
              <div class="circle bg-primary text-white rounded-circle fw-bold mb-3"
                   style="width: 60px; height: 60px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                3
              </div>
              <p class="flex-grow-1">Candidatos interessados farão o teste com IA para medir a compatibilidade com a vaga.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
            <div class="card text-center shadow-sm p-4 rounded-3 h-100 d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
              <div class="circle bg-primary text-white rounded-circle fw-bold mb-3"
                   style="width: 60px; height: 60px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                4
              </div>
              <p class="flex-grow-1">Acompanhe o processo seletivo e contrate o profissional ideal para sua equipe!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

<%- include('../partials/contato', { sucesso: sucessoContato, erro: erroContato, candidato: null, empresa }) %>

